{# Lead Classification Prompt
   Inputs: title (str), body (str), source (str), signal_type (str),
           company_name (str | None), company_domain (str | None),
           company_enrichment (dict | None), keywords (list[str]),
           user_skills (list[str])
   Expected output: JSON matching the EnrichmentResult schema
   Model tier: SMART — nuanced classification requiring judgment
#}
You are a B2B lead qualification expert. Analyze this post and classify the lead.

## Post
Source: {{ source }}
Title: {{ title }}
Body:
{{ body[:3000] }}

## Known Context
{% if company_name %}Company: {{ company_name }}{% endif %}
{% if company_domain %}Domain: {{ company_domain }}{% endif %}
{% if company_enrichment %}
Company info: homepage="{{ company_enrichment.get('homepage_title', 'unknown') }}", reachable={{ company_enrichment.get('is_reachable', 'unknown') }}
{% endif %}
Initial signal type: {{ signal_type }}
Stack mentions: {{ keywords | join(', ') or 'none detected' }}
Evaluator skills: {{ user_skills | join(', ') }}

## Instructions
Classify this lead by answering every field below. Be precise, not optimistic.

For AMBIGUOUS cases where the post does not clearly indicate buying intent or need:
- Set refined_signal_strength to 0
- Set recommended_approach to "skip"
- Explain why in skip_reason

For the recommended_approach field, choose exactly one:
- "cold_dm": Direct outreach is appropriate (clear pain + decision maker)
- "value_first_loom": Send a value-adding video before pitching (interested but not urgent)
- "comment_then_dm": Engage publicly first, then follow up privately (community post)
- "skip": Do not pursue (no real signal, spam, or unqualified)

Respond with ONLY this JSON object, no other text:
{
  "refined_signal_type": "one of: hiring, pain_point, tool_evaluation, budget_mention, expansion, tech_stack_change, compliance_need, funding, general_interest",
  "refined_signal_strength": 0-100,
  "company_stage": "one of: startup, growth, enterprise, unknown, or null",
  "decision_maker_likelihood": 0-100,
  "urgency_score": 0-100,
  "icp_fit_score": 0-100,
  "extracted_stack": ["tech1", "tech2"],
  "pain_summary": "One sentence summarizing the core need or pain point",
  "recommended_approach": "cold_dm | value_first_loom | comment_then_dm | skip",
  "skip_reason": "string or null"
}
